      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, and it runs like a total dream. I've taken great care of it, so it's ready to hit the road for its next adventure with you! Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this car is a perfect companion. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
