      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains taut thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded poly-bushings, complemented by Bilstein dampers for optimized rebound and compression. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical synchronization is superb. Recent preventative maintenance includes updated rod bearings and a valve adjustment, ensuring this M-division icon is ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
