    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride of ownership, offering a reliable and stylish driving experience. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains smoke-free and pristine; the leather seats are soft and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver's entry point. All technological features, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with a documented history of on-time oil changes and recent brake service. The alloy wheels are wrapped in high-quality tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a complete, honest package for a buyer seeking a dependable car that looks and drives beautifully.",
      "price": 32500.0,
